usecase "Extract Description Column" as U13
usecase "Extract Amount Column" as U14
usecase "Detect Income / Expense" as U15

usecase "Clean Transaction Data" as U16
usecase "Remove Empty Rows" as U17
usecase "Format Dates" as U18
usecase "Normalize Amounts" as U19
usecase "Clean Merchant Names" as U20

usecase "Auto-Categorize Transactions" as U21
usecase "Show Upload Preview" as U22
usecase "Confirm Before Saving" as U23
usecase "Save Transactions" as U24
